00:03:24.899 --> 00:03:26.669
among the British aristocracy.

00:03:27.709 --> 00:03:30.589
And this young Lord Lucan, although

00:03:30.769 --> 00:03:33.019
he wasn’t actually a Lord or a Lucan

00:03:33.019 --> 00:03:35.359
until his father died, this young man

00:03:35.479 --> 00:03:37.939
enjoyed a very privileged childhood.

00:03:38.769 --> 00:03:40.369
