00:03:42.779 --> 00:03:45.449
Lucan or simply Lucan throughout this

00:03:45.449 --> 00:03:47.639
episode, so as to avoid using two

00:03:47.639 --> 00:03:49.769
names to describe the same one man.

00:03:51.169 --> 00:03:53.239
