00:04:05.899 --> 00:04:07.479
When they eventually returned to

00:04:07.529 --> 00:04:10.279
England, however, the young Lord Lucan

00:04:10.669 --> 00:04:12.389
had a bit of a shock at the state of

00:04:12.389 --> 00:04:15.129
post-war England and bomb-ridden London.

00:04:16.239 --> 00:04:18.919
But for a young man like Lucan, he

00:04:18.919 --> 00:04:21.609
lived in a completely different world.

00:04:22.499 --> 00:04:24.519
He went to school at the prestigious

00:04:24.685 --> 00:04:26.539
Eton College, where he mingled

00:04:26.549 --> 00:04:28.589
with other society high-fliers and

00:04:28.839 --> 00:04:31.329
developed a taste for, a interest

00:04:31.329 --> 00:04:34.109
in, a vice that would remain with him

00:04:34.259 --> 00:04:36.639
