00:04:38.039 --> 00:04:39.859
As a young man, he was known to

00:04:39.869 --> 00:04:42.639
be charming, tall, and handsome,

00:04:42.989 --> 00:04:44.979
with a rather impressive moustache.

00:04:45.749 --> 00:04:48.729
