00:04:52.269 --> 00:04:54.459
enjoyed the ‘finer things in life’, we

00:04:54.479 --> 00:04:57.669
might say - fast cars, speedboats, the

00:04:57.859 --> 00:05:00.559
best wines and Russian vodkas, which

00:05:00.679 --> 00:05:03.019
were still pretty exotic at the time.

00:05:03.969 --> 00:05:06.829
Or as The New York Times put it, Lucan

00:05:06.829 --> 00:05:09.259
was - and I'm quoting directly - a

00:05:09.489 --> 00:05:12.109
